At Cambridge Square, YOU are our first priority.
We strive to uphold the highest standards in maintaining your apartment and the community.
Our experienced and caring staff goes the extra distance to make sure your needs are met.
You'll find an unmatched ambiance in our Victorian courtyards, English Tudor architecture, and poolside apartments.
Our convenient location puts downtown Seattle, the SeaTac airport, and SouthCenter shopping area within minutes while maintaining a very private and secure setting.
Come enjoy our garden style landscaping and two oversized resort style swimming pools with large deck areas for sun bathing and conversation.
Over half of our 201 apartments have views of the pools and most of those from private patios, porches.
Video tours and pictures are available upon request.
